But the only difference between you & me is I can tell you that I've died. This is the only difference between you and me. I know you won't believe me. This incident is just a month ago, a gang of boys burnt me alive. I was terribly asking for help but none saved me. People were recording videos so that they can show it to everyone. Suddenly someone complained the police, and the police came to search me. People also, out of fear supported those gang of boys and said that I've burnt myself. The police also accepted it. Police threw my body in a dirty, shady well. My body was fully burnt. After reading this message, even if you care your life, then frwd this message to 25 people. A boy named Rahul got this message. After he read this message he started laughing and ignored this message. When he was bathing, suddenly he heard me laughing. Quickly he took his Mobile and started messaging this to 25 people. But it was too late to do so. The next day when Rahul's mom came to his room, it was written with red blood, "NOW YOU WILL NEVER GET HIM BACK". Noone found him again because now he was with me. Similarly this message was sent to a Agra boy. Reading this message, as soon as he can sent it to 25 people. Now every second I look after him and safeguard him. Now send this message within the next 5 minutes to 25 people if you don't want your luck to be like Rahul. Your time starts now!!
